description: I think we were in Beijing for less than 48 hours (if you don't count the time wasted in-and-around airports).  在这个星期，北京飞机场很乱糟糟：two of the three airport runways were being renovated and, reportedly, there were thunderstorms as an excuse for the chaos, too.
creator: Jesse Gallagher
